<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="33" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1127,220,467]" pageId="4" pageNumber="33">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,280,284,307]" pageId="4" pageNumber="33">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species is named in honor of Dr. Saeid Eshghi, Associate Professor of Horticultural Sciences, Shiraz University who has helped me in identification of many plant materials for several years as well as in collecting the new species in this paper.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1127,220,467]" pageId="4" pageNumber="33">
